{"tid":999307,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港大學生會選舉 10%支持票便有機會當選","createTime":"2019-01-28T15:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T15:33:02.000Z","uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed70da3910ebfc2a765d2129c4f88a9a7935e9c","tid":999307,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:18:20.000Z","msg":"今日起一連五日將為週年大選投票日，候選單位包括候選內閣蒼傲、候選常務祕書麥嘉晉、校園電視候選內閣、學苑候選編輯委員會及候選普選評議員李嘉翹。<br />\n<br />\n根據學生會憲章第六章第七條(c)，候選人須符合3個條件方能當選：<br />\n<br />\n1, 支持票多於基本會員10%（即1688票支持票）<br />\n<br />\n2, 支持票多於反對票<br />\n<br />\n3, 支持票票數加反對票票數多於棄權票<br />\n2019年1月28日（星期一）至2月1日（星期五）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/photos/a.280176058717764/2079498858785466/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fphotos%2Fa.280176058717764%2F2079498858785466%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=9Xp0njqz6XOVojkP3vk5m0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=0825a7d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/photos/a.280176058717764/2079498858785466/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸學生要團結一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8045fd15e547d62bf10e0e67e1ae2d5b43ec770","tid":999307,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:23:41.000Z","msg":"截至晚上6時45分，共有10.12%選民（即約1,600人）就幹事會職位投票，數字已到達大選的法定人數門檻"},{"pid":"28dcd52a6ccd10cbe876abe1c4f19e7489fc3590","tid":999307,"uid":207005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"其實選到既可能性有幾高"}]}